    MapFactoryTest

    The MapFactoryTest test class is used to test the correctness of MapFactory which call the MapReader class to generate corresponding Map with the given input gameLevel

    • 方法详细资料

      • MapFactoryReturnTypeTest

        public void MapFactoryReturnTypeTest()
                              throws java.lang.Exception

        This is the test function that tests the correctness of MapFactory.createMap(String) which create the corresponding Map and return it

        This test will pass if the input is null, then not generate a Map. If the input is "NormalMode", it will generate a map.

        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - Throws the ClassNotFoundException if the constant class is not existed
